OL,3,CDerby County and Nottingham Forest
OL,4,Cmidfielder Henry Newton dies aged 82
OL,6,FDerby County have paid tribute to club
OL,7,Flegend, Henry Newton who has died at
OL,8,Fthe age of 82.
OL,10,FNewton played for the club for 16
OL,11,Fseasons, during which he helped them
OL,12,Fto win the 1974-1975 first division
OL,13,Ftitle.
OL,15,FHe was Brian Clough's last signing as
OL,16,FDerby manager.
OL,18,FNewton started his footballing career
OL,19,Fat Nottingham Forest in 1963 and
OL,20,Fplayed 282 league matches for them
OL,21,Fbefore leaving in 1970.
