OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776269466
OL,3,CDerby County and Nottingham Forest
OL,4,Cmidfielder Henry Newton dies aged 82
OL,6,FFormer teammate Roy McFarland paid
OL,7,Ftribute to Newton, hailing his
OL,8,Findustrious playing style and integral
OL,9,Frole in the squad.
OL,11,F"He was tenacious, his tackling was
OL,12,Fsecond to none," McFarland said.
OL,14,F"He dealt with things on the field; if
OL,15,Fanything went wrong, you just knew
OL,16,Fthat Henry Newton would do something
OL,17,Fin the match to support us as a team -
OL,18,Fhe was an excellent footballer.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@PO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776269466
OL,3,CDerby County and Nottingham Forest
OL,4,Cmidfielder Henry Newton dies aged 82
OL,6,F"Henry added that little bit of class,
OL,7,Fthat little bit of extra to the group,
OL,8,Fwhich made us a lot, lot stronger as a
OL,9,Fteam."
OL,11,FNewton played for the England under-23
OL,12,Fside on four occasions, making his
OL,13,Fdebut on 25 November 1964 against
OL,14,FRomania.
OL,16,FHe also played for Everton where he
OL,17,Fmade 85 senior appearances before
OL,18,Fleaving in 1973 and later for Walsall.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@FO]
